{
  "chapter": "077",
  "title": "魏公子列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "信陵君出身",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏公子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无忌</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭王</span>最小的儿子，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏安釐王</span>的异<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>弟。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭王</span>薨逝后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">安釐王</span>即位，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">信陵君</span>。当时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范睢</span>从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国逃往<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>，因怨恨<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏齐</span>的缘故，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大梁</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">华阳</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">下军</span>，击<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">走</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">芒卯</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>非常忧虑。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "礼贤下士致食客三千",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>为人仁厚而谦恭地对待<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人无论<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贤</span>能与否，都谦恭有<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">礼</span>地与之结交，不敢以自己的<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">富贵</span>骄待<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人因此从方圆<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千里</span>之外争相来投奔他，招致<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">食客</span>达<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三千人</span>之多。当时，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>因为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贤</span>能、门客众多，不敢<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">加兵</span>谋图<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国有<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十馀年（时长）</span>之久。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "赵王田猎",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王在下博戏，而北境传来举烽火的消息，说\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国寇兵将至，即将入境\"。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王丢下博戏，想召<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>商议。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>止住王说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王是在田猎而已，不是来侵寇。\" 又继续博戏如故。 王心中恐惧，心思不在博戏上。 过了一会儿，又从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">北方</span>传来消息说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王在打猎，不是来侵寇。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王大惊，说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>怎么知道的？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>的门客有能深入探知<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王隐秘之事的，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王所做的事，门客立刻来告知<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>因此得知。\" 此后<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王畏惧<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>的<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贤能</span>，不敢让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>担任国<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">政</span>。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "礼迎侯嬴",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国有个<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">隐士</span>叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯嬴</span>，年七十，家境贫寒，做<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大梁</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">夷门</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">监者</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>听说了，去拜访，想厚赠他。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯嬴</span>不肯接受，说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>修身洁行<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十年</span>，终究不因看门困顿而接受<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>的财物。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>于是摆设<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">酒</span>宴大会<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>。 宾客坐定，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>带着<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>骑，空出左边座位，亲自去迎接<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">夷门</span>的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>整理破旧的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣冠</span>，径直上车坐在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>的上座，不谦让，想借此观察<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>执<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">辔</span>驾车越发恭敬。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>又对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>有位朋友在市井屠户中，希望枉驾<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>骑去拜访他。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>驾车进入市井，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>下车去见他的朋友<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃亥</span>，故意斜视久立，与朋友谈话，暗中观察<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>神色越发和蔼。 这时，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将相</span>、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宗室</span>、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>坐满堂中，等<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>来举杯。 <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">巿人</span>都在观看<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>执<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">辔</span>驾车。 随从的骑从都暗中骂<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>神色始终不变，才告别朋友上车。 回到家，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>引<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>坐上座，遍指众<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>介绍，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>都惊讶。 <span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">酒</span>至酣时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>起身，到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>前祝寿。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>于是对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>说：\"<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">今日</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：侯嬴\">嬴（侯嬴）</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>做得够多了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：侯嬴\">嬴（侯嬴）</span>只是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">夷门</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">抱关者</span>罢了，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>亲自枉驾<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>骑，在众人广坐之中自己迎接<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：侯嬴\">嬴（侯嬴）</span>，不宜过分，现在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>特意如此。可<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：侯嬴\">嬴（侯嬴）</span>想要成就<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>的名声，所以故意让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>骑在市中久等，借路过的人来观看<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>越发恭敬。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">巿人</span>都认为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：侯嬴\">嬴（侯嬴）</span>是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">小人</span>，而认为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长者</span>能谦恭对待<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人。\" 于是酒罢，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>就成为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上客</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "访硃亥",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>所拜访的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">屠者</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃亥</span>，这个<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>是个<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贤</span>者，世人没有能了解他的，所以隐于屠间罢了。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>前去多次拜访他，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃亥</span>故意不回谢，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>感到奇怪。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "平原君求救",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏安釐王</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>已<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长平</span>军，又<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">进兵</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">姊</span>姐是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵惠文王</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>的夫人，多次给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>送来<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">书</span>信，向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>求<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">救</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋鄙</span>率<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十万众</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">救</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使者</span>告诉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王说：\"我<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国旦暮可下，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>谁敢<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">救</span>援，攻<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>后，必定移兵先<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>他。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王恐惧，派人阻止<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋鄙</span>，让他驻军在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄴</span>，名义上<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">救</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，实际是两端观望。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使者</span>车马前后相接来到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国，责备<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏公子</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胜\">胜（赵胜）</span>之所以与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>结为婚姻，是因为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>道义高尚，能急人之困。现在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>旦暮之间将降<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>的<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">救</span>兵不到，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>能急人之困的意义何在！况且<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>纵然看轻<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵胜\">胜（赵胜）</span>，抛弃我投降<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国，难道不怜惜<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">姊</span>姐吗？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>忧虑，多次请求<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王，以及让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">辩士</span>用尽各种办法劝说王。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王畏惧<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国，终究不听<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>自己估量终究不能说服王，心想不能独自活着而让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国灭亡，就邀集<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>，凑集<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>骑<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百馀乘</span>，打算带着门客前往赴<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国一同赴死。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "侯嬴献计",
      "text": "出发经过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">夷门</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>去见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>，把自己将赴死<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军的情形都告诉了他。 告辞要走，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>努力吧，老<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>不能跟从。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>走了<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数里</span>，心中不快，说：\"我待<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>周备之至，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>没有人不知道，现在我将死，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>却没有一言半语送我，我难道有什么失礼之处吗？\" 又引<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>返回，去问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>笑着说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>本来就知道<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>会回来。\" 说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>喜好<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人，名闻<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>。现在有难，没有别的办法就想去赴<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军，好比把肉投给饥饿的<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">虎</span>，有什么功效呢？那还要门客做什么？然而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>待<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>深厚，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>前行而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>不相送，所以知道<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>心中有怨会回来。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>再拜，于是请教。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>就屏退旁人悄悄说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：侯嬴\">嬴（侯嬴）</span>听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋鄙</span>的兵<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">符</span>经常放在王的卧室内，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">如姬</span>最得宠，可以出入王的卧室，有能力<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">窃</span>取兵符。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：侯嬴\">嬴（侯嬴）</span>听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">如姬</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>亲被人<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>害，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">如姬</span>为此求报仇<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三年</span>，从王以下想替她父亲报仇的都没能办到。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">如姬</span>向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>哭诉，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>派门客<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>下仇人的头，恭敬地献给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">如姬</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">如姬</span>愿为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>去死，义不容辞，只是苦于没有机会罢了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>果真开口请求<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">如姬</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">如姬</span>必定答应，就能得到虎<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">符</span>去〖[夺<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋鄙</span>的军队，北去<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">救</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>而向西〖[卻<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军，这是<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五霸</span>之<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>的功业啊。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>听从他的计策，请求<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">如姬</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">如姬</span>果然〖[盗出<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋鄙</span>的兵<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">符</span>交给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "椎杀晋鄙",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>要出发，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将</span>在外，主君的命令有所不受，以便利国家。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>即使合<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">符</span>，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋鄙</span>不把兵权授予<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>而再请示王，事情必危。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>的朋友屠者<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃亥</span>可以同行，这人是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">力士</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋鄙</span>听从，最好；不听，可让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃亥</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>他。\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>流泪。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>怕死吗？为什么流泪呢？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋鄙</span>是个大声呼喝的老<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将</span>，去了恐怕不听令，必定要<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>他，因此流泪，难道是怕死吗？\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>去请<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃亥</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃亥</span>笑着说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>只是市井鼓刀的屠者，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>亲自数次问候<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>之所以不回拜致谢，是认为小<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">礼</span>没有用。现在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>有急，这正是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>效命之时。\" 于是与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>同行。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>过去向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>辞行。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>本应跟从，年老不能。请计算<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>行程的日子，到达<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋鄙</span>军的那天，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>向北自〖[刭，以送<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>于是上路。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "救邯郸存赵",
      "text": "到了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄴</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">矫<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王命令〖[代替<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋鄙</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋鄙</span>合<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">符</span>，感到怀疑，举手看着<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>说：\"现在我拥〖$十万之众</span>，屯驻在边境上，国之重任，现在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>单<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>来替<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">代，这是怎么回事？\" 想不听从。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃亥</span>从袖中拿出〖$四十斤</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">铁椎</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">椎<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋鄙</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>于是统领<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋鄙</span>的军队。 整顿军队下令军中说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>都在军中的，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>回去；<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>都在军中的，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄</span>回去；独生<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>没有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>的，回家奉养父母。\" 得到精兵〖$八万人</span>，进兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军解围退去，于是<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">救</span>了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">存了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>亲自到边境迎接<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>背着箭袋<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">矢</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>在前引路。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王再拜说：\"自古以来〖_贤</span>人中没有比得上<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>的。\" 在此时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>不敢把自己与任何人相比。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>诀别，到了军中那天，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯生</span>果然向北自〖[刭。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "留赵受封辞让",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王恼怒<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">盗其兵<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">符</span>，〖[矫命<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋鄙</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>自己也知道。已经〖[卻<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>〖[存<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>之后，派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将</span>领兵归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>独自与门客留在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝成王</span>感念<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>〖[矫命〖[夺<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋鄙</span>军从而〖[存<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，就与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>商议，以〖$五城</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>听说后，心中骄傲自负而有居功之色。有门客劝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>说：\"事物有不可忘的，有不可不忘的。别人对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">德</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>不可忘；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>对别人有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">德</span>，希望<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>忘掉。况且<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">矫<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王的命令，〖[夺<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋鄙</span>之兵以<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">救</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>是有功，对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>则算不得<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">忠臣</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>竟然自傲居功，私下认为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>这样做。\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>立即自责，似乎无地自容。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王打扫道路亲自迎接，执主人之<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">礼</span>，引<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>登西阶。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>侧身行走推辞谦让，从东阶而上。自说有罪过，对不起<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>无功。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王侍<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">酒</span>到晚上，终究没开口献〖$五城</span>，因为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>的退让。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>最终留在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王以<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄗</span>作为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>的汤沐邑，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国也再以<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">信陵</span>奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>留在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "从毛公薛公游",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>听说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">处士</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">毛公</span>藏身于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">博徒</span>之中，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薛公</span>藏身于卖浆人家，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>想见这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">两人</span>，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">两人</span>自己躲藏不肯见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>打听到他们的住处，就步行前去结交这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">两人</span>，相处甚欢。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>听说后，对他夫人说：\"起初我听说夫人的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>无双，如今我听说他竟随意和<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">博徒</span>、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">卖浆者</span>交游，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>只是个妄人罢了。\" 夫人把话告诉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>就辞别夫人要走，说：\"起初我听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贤</span>能，所以辜负<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王而<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">救</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，以此称赞<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>的交游，只是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">豪举</span>而已，不是真求<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无忌</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大梁</span>时，就常听说这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">两人</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贤</span>能，到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国，只怕不能见到他们。让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无忌</span>去结交他们，尚且怕他们不愿理我，现在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>竟以此为羞，他不足以交游。\" 于是整理行装要走。夫人把话告诉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>就免<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">冠</span>谢罪，坚决挽留<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>的门下人听说了，有一半离开<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>投奔<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人又来投奔<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>使<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span>的门客倾心归附。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "毛薛劝归救魏",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>留在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十年（时长）</span>没有回国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，日夜出兵东<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王忧虑，派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使</span>者去请<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>怕王怨怒自己，于是告诫门下说：\"有敢替<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使</span>者通报的，处死。\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>都背弃<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国来到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国，没有人敢劝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>回国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">毛公</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薛公</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">两人</span>去见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>之所以在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国受到重视，名闻<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，只因有<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国。现在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>急迫而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>不顾念，让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大梁</span>而<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">夷</span>平<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宗庙</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>还有什么面目立于<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>？\" 话还没说完，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>立刻变色，吩咐备<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>急驾回国<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">救</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "率五国破秦",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王见到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>，相对流泪，把<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上将军</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>交给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>于是担任上将军。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏安釐王</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三十年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使</span>者遍告<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>担任将军，各派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将</span>领兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">救</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>率<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五国</span>的军队，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河外</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军，击<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">走</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙骜</span>。于是乘胜<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">逐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军直到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">函谷关</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">抑止<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>兵，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>兵不敢出关。在此时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>威震〖_天下</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>的门客进献<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">兵法</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>都署上他们的名字，所以世俗称为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏公子</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">兵法</span>。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "病酒而卒",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王忧虑，就拿<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万斤</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国行贿，寻找<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋鄙</span>的门客，让他们在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王前诋毁<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>，说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>流亡在外<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十年（时长）</span>了，现在做<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将</span>领都归属他，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>只听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏公子</span>，不听说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>也想趁此时机南面称王，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>畏惧<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>的声威，正想共同拥立他。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>多次派反间伪装祝贺<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>是否已立为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王日日听到毁谤，不能不信，后来果然派人〖[代<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>领军。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>自己知道再次因毁谤被废，就谢绝称病不朝，与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>整夜饮酒，喝醇<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">酒</span>，多亲近<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妇女</span>。日夜纵酒作乐<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">四岁（时长）</span>，最终因酒病而去世。那一年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏安釐王</span>也薨逝。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "秦灭魏",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>死了，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蒙骜</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>下<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十城</span>，初次设置<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东郡</span>。此后<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国逐渐蚕食<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十八岁</span>后<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">虏</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">屠</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大梁</span>。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "高祖祭公子",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>年轻微时，多次听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贤</span>能。等到即<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>位，每次经过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大梁</span>，常祭祀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十二年（时长）</span>，从讨<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span>回来，为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>安置守冢<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五家</span>，世世代代按<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四时</span>祭祀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：我经过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大梁</span>的废墟，打听所谓的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">夷门</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">夷门</span>是城的东门。<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>各<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>也有喜好<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人的，但<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">信陵君</span>接纳<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">岩穴隐者</span>，不以下交为耻，是有缘故的。名冠<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，并非虚传。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>每经过都命令<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众祭祀不绝。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：信陵君\">信陵（信陵君）</span>下<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>，邻国相倾。 以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子</span>故，不敢<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">加兵</span>。 颇知<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃亥</span>，尽<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">礼</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯嬴</span>。 遂<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">卻</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋鄙</span>，终辞<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>城。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：毛公\">毛（毛公）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：薛公\">薛（薛公）</span>见重，万古希声。"
    }
  }
}